## [Direct link to heading](https://www.docs.hyperbrowser.ai/web-scraping/scrape\#usage)    Usage

NodePythoncURL

Copy

```inline-grid min-w-full grid-cols-[auto_1fr] p-2 [count-reset:line]
import { Hyperbrowser } from "@hyperbrowser/sdk";
import { config } from "dotenv";

config();

const client = new Hyperbrowser({
  apiKey: process.env.HYPERBROWSER_API_KEY,
});

const main = async () => {
  // Handles both starting and waiting for scrape job response
  const scrapeResult = await client.scrape.startAndWait({
    url: "https://example.com",
  });
  console.log("Scrape result:", scrapeResult);
};

main();
```

